FBIS3-14741 "drsov039_e_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs U.S. Begins Aid for Dismantling Nuclear Weapons LD2502155894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1517 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502155894 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Kiev February 25 UKRINFORM-TASS -- The United States has begun implementing its aid programme to Ukraine within the frame of the agreement on Safety and Security in Dismantling Nuclear Weapons in Ukraine (SSD). This agreement was signed by the U.S. and Ukraine in October of last year. The American aid has arrived in the form of fuel for transportation and for the operation of equipment to be used in the dismantling of Ukraine's nuclear weapons.
